tent",\n      "type": "string"\n    }\n  },\n  "required": [\n    "filename",\n    "directory",\n    "overwrite",\n    "content"\n  ],\n  "title": "FileWriterToolInput",\n  "type": "object",\n  "additionalProperties": false\n}\nTool Description: A tool to write content to a specified file. Accepts filename, content, and optionally a directory path and overwrite flag as input.\nTool Name: Read a file\'s content\nTool Arguments: {\n  "description": "Input for FileReadTool.",\n  "properties": {\n    "file_path": {\n      "description": "Mandatory file full path to read the file",\n      "title": "File Path",\n      "type": "string"\n    },\n    "start_line": {\n      "anyOf": [\n        {\n          "type": "integer"\n        },\n        {\n          "type": "null"\n        }\n      ],\n      "default": 1,\n      "description": "Line number to start reading from (1-indexed)",\n      "title": "Start Line"\n    },\n    "line_count": {\n      "anyOf": [\n        {\n          "type": "integer"\n        },\n        {\n          "type": "null"\n        }\n      ],\n      "default": null,\n      "description": "Number of lines to read. If None, reads the entire file",\n      "title": "Line Count"\n    }\n  },\n  "required": [\n    "file_path",\n    "start_line",\n    "line_count"\n  ],\n  "title": "FileReadToolSchema",\n  "type": "object",\n  "additionalProperties": false\n}\nTool Description: A tool that reads the content of a file. To use this tool, provide a \'file_path\' parameter with the path to the file you want to read. Optionally, provide \'start_line\' to start reading from a specific line and \'line_count\' to limit the number of lines read.\nTool Name: List files in directory\nTool Arguments: {\n  "description": "Input for FixedDirectoryReadTool.",\n  "properties": {},\n  "title": "FixedDirectoryReadToolSchema",\n  "type": "object",\n  "additionalProperties": false\n}\nTool Description: A tool that can be used to list /Users/xiao/Documents/python/crewai_mas_demo/m3l19/workspace\'s content.\n\nIMPORTANT: Use the following format in your response:\n\n```\nThought: you should always think about what to do\nAction: the action to take, only one name of [search_web, Read website content, File Writer Tool, Read a file\'s content, List files in directory], just the name, exactly as it\'s written.\nAction Input: the input to the action, just a simple JSON object, enclosed in curly braces, using " to wrap keys and values.\nObservation: the result of the action\n```\n\nOnce all necessary information is gathered, return the following format:\n\n```\nThought: I now know the final answer\nFinal Answer: the final answer to the original input question\n```'}]
2026-03-31 14:26:51 - llm.aliyun_llm - INFO - 收到 LLM API 响应  result={'choices': [{'finish_reason': 'stop', 'index': 0, 'message': {'content': '```\nThought: 已经识别出极客时间平台上与多智能体相关的核心课程，包括用户自己的《企业级多智能体设计实战》以及《LLaMA 3前沿模型实战课》和《MCP & A2A 前沿实战》中的相关章节。虽然直接抓取课程介绍页只能获得标题，但结合搜索结果的摘要信息已足够构建调研报告。现在需要将这些信息整理成结构化报告并保存。\nAction: File Writer Tool\nAction Input: {"filename": "极客时间多智能体课程现状调研报告.md", "directory": "./", "overwrite": true, "content": "# 极客时间多智能体课程现状调研报告\\n\\n## 背景与定义\\n\\n多智能体系统（Multi-Agent System, MAS）是当前AI工程化领域的热点方向，旨在通过多个具备特定技能的智能体协同工作，解决复杂任务。极客时间作为面向IT从业者的在线学习平台，已推出多门涵盖此主题的课程。\\n\\n## 当前现状\\n\\n根据调研，极客时间平台上与多智能体直接相关的课程和内容主要包括：\\n\\n| 课程/专栏名称 | 类型 | 核心内容摘要 | 链接 |\\n| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |\\n| **企业级多智能体设计实战** | 专栏课程 | 由晓寒主讲，聚焦于体系化的Multi-Agent设计模式和企业级全链路工程能力。课程内容覆盖从需求分析、系统设计到线上可观测性和数据飞轮迭代的完整交付视角，并包含4大高价值场景实践案例。 | https://time.geekbang.org/course/intro/101114301 |\\n| **LLaMA 3前沿模型实战课** | 专栏文章 | 其中第16讲《如何利用LLaMA 3实现多智能体协作？》探讨了多智能体系统的必要性（如权限控制、多方协作）、设计原则（如单一职责、上下文隔离）及其带来的效率优势。 | https://time.geekbang.org/column/article/825791 |\\n| **MCP & A2A 前沿实战** | 专栏文章 | 其中第16讲《双剑合璧：MCP和A2A联合构建智能Agents系统》通过实操，使用`python-a2a`库构建具备A2A通信与MCP工具调用能力的智能Agent系统。 | https://time.geekbang.org/column/article/891156 |\\n| **DeepResearch前沿智能体实战** | 专栏课程 | 课程标题明确包含“智能体”和“A2A”等关键词，内容涉及大模型、AI应用开发、多模态、RAG、LangGraph等前沿技术。 | https://time.geekbang.org/course/intro/101074901 |\\n\\n此外，在极客时间的训练营产品线中，也出现了“企业级 Agent 开发实战营”、“多模态 Agent 开发实战营”等以Agent为核心的教学产品，显示出平台对此方向的重视和投入。\\n\\n## 关键趋势\\n\\n1.  **从概念到工程落地**：平台上的课程内容正从早期的概念普及（如什么是Agent）转向更深入的工程化实践，强调企业级应用所需的稳定性、可观测性和可维护性。\\n2.  **聚焦核心模式与框架**：课程普遍关注多智能体系统的核心设计模式（如上下文隔离、分工协作）以及主流框架（如CrewAI, LangGraph）的应用。\\n3.  **与前沿协议结合**：多智能体课程内容常与MCP（Model Context Protocol）、A2A（Agent-to-Agent）等新兴通信协议结合，教授如何构建可互操作的智能体系统。\\n4.  **强调实战与案例**：无论是专栏还是训练营，都高度强调动手实践，通过具体的高价值场景案例来贯穿教学。\\n\\n## 结论与建议\\n\\n极客时间平台已形成较为清晰的多智能体/AI智能体课程矩阵，覆盖了从基础理论、核心框架到企业级工程实践的多个层面。用户正在开发的《企业级多智能体设计实战》课程定位精准，填补了市场对于体系化、工程化多智能体设计方法论的需求空白。\\n\\n建议在后续课程开发中，可进一步突出与竞品课程的差异化，例如更深入地剖析CrewAI等框架的源码级实现，或提供更多关于生产环境中智能体系统治理（如安全护栏、评测体系）的独特见解。"}', 'role': 'assistant'}}], 'created': 1774938380, 'id': 'chatcmpl-a43a21ff-0c58-9333-8130-b12950df51b9', 'model': 'qwen3-max', 'object': 'chat.completion', 'usage': {'completion_tokens': 1010, 'prompt_tokens': 14376, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'cached_tokens': 11392}, 'total_tokens': 15386}}
